    <item>
      <title>据日经新闻报道，东芝将在最新重组计划中裁员 5,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/toshiba-to-cut-5-000-jobs-in-latest-bid-to-restructure-nikkei</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《日经新闻》周三表示，东芝公司计划在日本裁员 5,000 人，约占其国内员工总数的十分之一，以削减成本并专注于基础设施和数字技术业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/toshiba-to-cut-5-000-jobs-in-latest-bid-to-restructure-nikkei</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:25:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚航空希望减轻中东绕行航班的飞机负载</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-air-looks-to-lighten-plane-loads-on-middle-east-detour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗周末对以色列的袭击迫使航空公司绕道而行，马来西亚航空公司将暂时停止从吉隆坡飞往伦敦的客运航班运送货物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/malaysia-air-looks-to-lighten-plane-loads-on-middle-east-detour</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:11:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非通胀放缓，不太可能引发降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/south-african-inflation-cools-to-two-month-low-in-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的通胀率在三月份跌至两个月低点，但这不太可能说服政策制定者削减借贷成本，因为由于油价上涨和兰特再度疲软，预计通胀率下降将是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/south-african-inflation-cools-to-two-month-low-in-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:03:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vinci 将购买英国爱丁堡机场的大部分扩建</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/vinci-agrees-to-buy-edinburgh-airport-for-1-27-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vinci 同意以 12.7 亿英镑（16 亿美元）购买爱丁堡机场的多数股权，进一步推动这家法国建筑和特许经营公司在英国的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/vinci-agrees-to-buy-edinburgh-airport-for-1-27-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:10:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
