    <item>
      <title>受冲突风险影响，亚洲天然气价格上涨至 2024 年最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/asian-gas-prices-surge-near-highest-this-year-amid-conflict-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心以色列周末对伊朗袭击的反应可能会演变成更广泛的冲突，亚洲液化天然气价格跃升至一月初以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/asian-gas-prices-surge-near-highest-this-year-amid-conflict-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
